    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造独特殖民地</strong></h2><br>踏入 Colony，一个融合生存与策略的引人入胜的游戏。通过 <strong>建造</strong>、<strong>生存</strong>，以及进行史诗般的 <strong>探索之旅</strong> 来塑造您的命运。您的选择不仅塑造您的殖民地，还影响周围的世界。准备好踏上创造与 <strong>发现之旅</strong>！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>等待您的是什么</strong></h2><br>想象一个殖民地 <strong>蓬勃发展并成长</strong> 的领域，那就是 Colony。在这款游戏中，您 <strong>收集资源</strong>，创造关键的 <strong>工具</strong>，并 <strong>保卫您的人民</strong>。成为一个 <strong>领导者</strong>，在这里，每个选择都会产生影响，成长无界限。善良还是 <strong>果断</strong>，结盟还是 <strong>开拓未知领域</strong> – 您的决策将引导您的命运。您和您的盟友能否培育出最非凡的殖民地？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>拓展您的视野</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/f626b3ca5b4ddf4bef8875b294bfc3d3.poster.avif?t=1715330515\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/f626b3ca5b4ddf4bef8875b294bfc3d3.webm?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/f626b3ca5b4ddf4bef8875b294bfc3d3.mp4?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在郁郁葱葱的 <strong>森林</strong> 和宁静的 <strong>水域</strong> 中，您将揭示 <strong>生存的艺术</strong>。然而，荒野并不是您唯一的画布。探索 <strong>新的岛屿</strong>，每个岛屿都是 <strong>等待被开发的资源宝库</strong>。乘船冒险，展开对未知海域的探索。每个岛屿都提供 <strong>独特的宝藏</strong> – 您通向 <strong>繁荣之路</strong>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>物流与贸易</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/b11b077bd6b7a11461cebb2c9660e44e.poster.avif?t=1715330515\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/b11b077bd6b7a11461cebb2c9660e44e.webm?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/b11b077bd6b7a11461cebb2c9660e44e.mp4?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>扩展带来了一个新的挑战 – <strong>运输</strong>。建立 <strong>物流网络</strong> 来 <strong>在岛屿之间运输资源</strong>。建设 <strong>港口</strong> 进行高效的 <strong>贸易和资源交换</strong>。每个岛屿的优势 <strong>弥补了其他岛屿的弱点</strong>，创造出一个充满活力的 <strong>繁荣生态系统</strong>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多样的结构</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/a91d35bcefaa2f7194162920a806eb5a.poster.avif?t=1715330515\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/a91d35bcefaa2f7194162920a806eb5a.webm?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/a91d35bcefaa2f7194162920a806eb5a.mp4?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>打造 <strong>多样的结构</strong> – 从繁忙的 <strong>工厂</strong> 到坚固的 <strong>防御工事</strong>。工厂充满活力，<strong>工人创造商品</strong>。物流中心和储存库 <strong>保障资源</strong>，而防御设施则 <strong>守护着竞争对手的野心</strong>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>您的殖民地的居民</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/bb4da84205ca40cf394e769672e86bf8.poster.avif?t=1715330515\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/bb4da84205ca40cf394e769672e86bf8.webm?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/bb4da84205ca40cf394e769672e86bf8.mp4?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您的殖民地 <strong>依靠其居民茁壮成长</strong>。每个居民带来 <strong>独特的优势和技能</strong>。分配角色以 <strong>最大程度地提高效率和和谐</strong>，让您繁忙的定居点焕发生机。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>参与战略战争</strong></h2><br>组织 <strong>征服</strong>，并 <strong>防御</strong>，因为 <strong>对手出现</strong>。集结 <strong>军队</strong>，制定策略，从上方 <strong>指挥</strong>。警惕的防御将成为您的 <strong>堡垒</strong>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>铸就胜利的联盟</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/64b9482bd0c5c815ba74519fc2c2ec36.poster.avif?t=1715330515\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/64b9482bd0c5c815ba74519fc2c2ec36.webm?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017050/extras/64b9482bd0c5c815ba74519fc2c2ec36.mp4?t=1715330515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>招募多达 <strong>4名玩家</strong>，以 <strong>巩固您的殖民地</strong>。研究员、战士等 – <strong>伙伴丰富您的旅程</strong>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备创立您的传奇吗？</strong></h2><br>拥抱 Colony 的冒险 – 一个关于 <strong>成长、领导和探索的故事</strong>。加入这个旅程， <strong>塑造您的殖民地</strong>，并沉浸于 <strong>无限可能的世界</strong>。现在将 Colony 添加到 <strong>心愿单中</strong>",
